{"tid":1843363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳偉霆春晚唱《過年disco》:「無論走到哪裡，你永遠都是中國人。」","createTime":"2020-01-26T07:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T08:08:49.000Z","uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"739fa961410b9f8f276c4842b5f4c503d1ab4121","tid":1843363,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:29:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UsMh1FxpNpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUsMh1FxpNpc&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGemINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=5e013f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UsMh1FxpNpc</a><br />\n<br />\n陳偉霆早前憑騎呢廣東話口音唱《野狼Disco》令人氣再升，日前獲邀為央視《春節聯歡晚會》錄影，夥拍張藝興和《野狼》原唱者寶石Gem獻唱重新編寫的《過年disco》。穿上紅色皮褸配黑tee黑褲的陳偉霆，以騎呢腔演唱，而張藝興及寶石Gem則負責rap，三人又載歌載舞合唱：「一定不要忘記，無論走到那裏，你永遠都是中國人。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200126/large/1579957743_7842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200126%2Flarge%2F1579957743_7842.jpg&h=84e8623c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e7e894d2d2e788d0b0e6c44a221b48ed32ecfed","tid":1843363,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200126/ZT2IG2WBMH7DU7DRO5KNGW6A5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200126%2FZT2IG2WBMH7DU7DRO5KNGW6A5I%2F&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGemINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=957f7eea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200126%2FZT2IG2WBMH7DU7DRO5KNGW6A5I%2F&h=502013de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200126/ZT2IG2WBMH7DU7DRO5KNGW6A5I/</a>"},{"pid":"6ee491fa84cf84bccd805884e135aca37054207a","tid":1843363,"uid":82628,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"啱 佢